<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> - MonEntreprise</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'><text y='.9em' font-size='90'>🏢</text></svg>">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <a href="/" class="nav-brand">🏢 MonEntreprise</a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/">Accueil</a></li>
                <li><a href="/services">Nos Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact">Contactez-nous</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="error-page">
                <h1>404</h1>
                <h2 style="color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Page Non Trouvée</h2>
                
                <div style="font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">🔍</div>
                
                <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #666;">
                    Oops ! La page que vous recherchez semble avoir disparu...
                </p>
                
                <div style="background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 15px; margin: 2rem 0;">
                    <h3>🧭 Où souhaitez-vous aller ?</h3>
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 1rem;">
                        <a href="/" class="btn">🏠 Accueil</a>
                        <a href="/services" class="btn">💼 Nos Services</a>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn">📞 Contact</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
                    <button onclick="history.back()" class="btn" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #95a5a6, #7f8c8d);">
                        ← Retour
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 MonEntreprise. Tous droits réservés.</p>
        <p>Heures d'ouverture : Lundi - Vendredi, 9h00 - 17h00</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>